Package org.sparadrap.model.PurchaseModel

Class Purchase

java.lang.Object
org.sparadrap.model.PurchaseModel.Purchase
public class Purchase extends Object
Represents a purchase of medicines. Can be associated with a prescription or be a direct purchase without one.
